Introduction of data changes,  risks and opportunities; development of  data awareness.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The student understands the changes in the data society and the risks and opportunities associated with them.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student:  - understands the most important concepts and developments regarding data collection and analysis in the digital age;  - associates the meaning of changes in data collection and its use in the society;  - understands data development in the improvement of public services in Estonia in the international comparative context;  - describes data protection developments in Estonia and the European Union, including with regard to young people;  - explains the importance of data awareness for young people and in the organization;  - assesses the risks and opportunities associated with data collection and protection in one's  work.
